,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9d48bdffe059ccfd364efb73f05f468554299f93","tid":812583,"uid":72690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6104a5ef1dcd239ff820bb2a2c5f2c0f37b8883","tid":812583,"uid":137706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ceaa4c30e7ec88e154b62d8d359d38dbfc84deff","tid":812583,"uid":72690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:15:12.000Z","msg":"我諗我有排受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:17:23.000Z","msg":"我都就一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />雖然無一開始咁辛苦 <br />\n但仲係日日都會諗起佢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:18:53.000Z","msg":"巴打點move on"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:35:53.000Z","msg":"因為太深刻所以我選擇以毒攻毒<br />\n日日聽失戀歌不論本地中國<br />\n迫自己記起所有野之後爆喊一場<br />\n等你以後就算無啦啦記得你都唔會再有太大反應<br />\n<br />\n每次喊完記得同返自己講:你愛既只係以前既佢<br />\n我知係會唔捨得唔想放手好唔甘心，但係屬於你嗰個佢已經唔喺度，就算以後佢點都好，嗰個佢只有你擁有過，你咪當有段開心回憶。<br />\n<br />\n屬於你既佢咪由佢係回憶入面得閒拎出黎懷緬下，但一定唔可以擺係心度，學識同習慣唔再在乎。將多出黎既時間投放係朋友、事業或者打機上面，最緊要係唔好做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"8421f9833f866196054f3b9014dc7959f44f759f","tid":812583,"uid":195950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c395a317897f456c7d81e2fc04a2c5b3480bbe3a","tid":812583,"uid":72690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T17:53:38.000Z","msg":"放唔低既你地又會點做啊？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:37:24.000Z","msg":"終於？即係你等咗好耐，好想分手？"},{"pid":"2cef110023719a4a9ae7a4b70ce453ed9dd52c07","tid":812583,"uid":20772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:41:31.000Z","msg":"好彩走得早"},{"pid":"7c31be703bc11e328c6d1ddd8160a5bace2f7df5","tid":812583,"uid":40652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T18:44:23.000Z","msg":"2年就算啦"},{"pid":"761343603cc5bb2bd44d3af27c5c27b53cbd4ed2","tid":812583,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim